*First place winner for AnB CS:S map competition*

de_archive
jamiemanson@skeebz.com
SkeebzDotCom
www.skeebz.com

for mapcontest @
www.ctrclan.com
Assault 'n' Battery

de_archive is a CS:S version of a CS 1.6 map concept I did in the early years, I was sad that the map was poorly textured and detailed
for such a good concept of a map. Lying around 
in the dusty pockets of my old HDD I have 
ressurrected it and completely remade it from 
scratch using basic layouts of the old map.

Now with Hl2 I have built the map up again
using the basic structure of the old map I had.
Noticable difference, if not so obvious to 
make the map look like an archive. Most
people thought it was a Goldeneye remake.

So delve into the deep unknown map which is
DE_ARCHIVE

Story:
	I dunno... The terrorists don't like
archives, reading or paper. Man, I hate paper so
bad!

notes:
 
The mp3 radio station will disappear if you leave 
the radius of it. No idea why, there's no fix without
changing it to a 45 meg wav file :]
